}{}$$K = K_s \times T_s/T + K_n \times T_n / T$$\end{document}K=Ks×Ts/T+Kn×Tn/Twhere T is the time since the split from the last common ancestor (LCA). By selecting the lower and upper bound of the confidence interval for the species divergence time T, which was obtained from TimeTree website (http://www.timetree.org/) to estimate a lower and upper bound for Tn as:
